data.text:
Privilege and Tale of Us have today laid out a stonkingly good line-up for the duo's final Afterlife party in Ibiza this month.

The in-demand duo are looking to close out a successful debut season at the world's biggest club with a bang.

Taking place on Thursday 28th September, Tale of Us will be playing alongside the likes of Dixon, Nina Kraviz, Rødhåd, Solomum, Vaal and many more.

The closing party will see the entirety of the club open, with the cavernous main room, dubbed the Hall, being adorned with the usual Afterlife stage production.

The Italian duo with be playing both in the Hall and in the Vista alongside Mind Against and Recondite, whilst the intimate Chamber will host Alex.Do, Dennis Horvat and Vaal.
